info.help_text:
This report gives information about GTP-C v2 create session response messages sent per cause code on S11 interface (MME <- SGW).
Use case specific instructions:
- This report can be used to troubleshoot the 'Create Session Request received on S11 interface' messages;
- Note, 'Ratio' column is applicable on GV211 level only.
